import Splash from "../layout/Splash";

let pageTitle = {
  "title": "Byte Digital - Digital Creative Services"
}

const Home = () => ( <
  Splash data = {
    pageTitle
  } >
  <
  main >

  <
  div className = "container text-center" >
  <
  div className = "hero-content style1" >
  <
  h1 className = " text-white" >
  We are a digital < br / > creative agency <
  /h1> <
  h4 className = "text-lowercase text-white font-weight-normal" >
  creating web and mobile services and solutions
  for businesses and brands. <
  /h4> <
  /div> <
  /div>

  <
  /main> <
  /Splash>
);

export default Home;
